					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It doesn't remap the RAM. Parts of the ROM that map to areas occupied by internal memory, such as banks $7E and $7F and the first half of banks $00-$3F and $80-$BF, are just made inaccessible by the address decoder.</div>

